array:12 [
  "_token" => "uFrftbQzssRn7mj59V3fkTJjVlY4PzBPr0epDhFt"
  "title" => "The Generational Divide: Why Millennials Still Love Drive-Thrus While Gen Z Parks and Walks"
  "content" => """
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"> </p>\r\n
    <p> </p>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The rapidly changing culture of today shapes our interaction with common conveniences depending on our generation. From eating to travel choices, Millennials and Gen Z typically approach life in rather different ways. Their different perspectives on drive-throughs and parking provide one amazing illustration of this split. </span></p>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-94801b88-7fff-b61a-993a-39c3e2634a8c"><span style="border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 378px; height: 71px;"><img style="margin-left: auto; margin-top: -636.002px; display: block; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfRMXIhYogiYtXjoYeIQcYi-AFZFLPJZYBqF_iRCtlgiyj-9qoYQBFor-S7MMXfwCEzw4rR-X_oSu682SqfkP0mVLCAXASmz_1seaxYBBt9vv0sI68qTk1Q1Lp_nW0z3Bxb2_fD1Jevp7BUJrqxXQ?key=4Vjsx6U4GLkna1kvCU3Umqhe" width="752.2986904430203" height="1338.360037700283" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"> </p>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-268c8a6f-7fff-6f2d-1399-ad83194a4d9a" style="color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: collapse;"><span style="border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 626px; height: 418px;"><img style="margin-top: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/uploads/0000/1/2025/02/22/unnamed-1.jpg" width="626" height="418" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">While Gen Z is more likely to park their cars and stroll, Millennial still value the drive-through ease. The post covers the causes of this generational difference and looks at how East Midlands Airport Parking, EMA Parking, and Meet & Greet East Midlands Airport satisfy these different desires.</span></p>\r\n
    <h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Drive-Thru Phenomenon: A Millennial Favorite</span></h2>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Born between 1981 and 1996, millennial grew up between the golden age of drive-thru and fast-food culture. Drive-thru for this generation stand for convenience, efficiency, and a bit of nostalgia rather than only a means of a quick lunch.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1. Convenience is King</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Millennial have become famous for their hectic schedules, juggling jobs, families, and social life. Eliminating the need to park, walk, and wait in line, drive-through at </span><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="/"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #0563c1; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">EMA Parking</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> provides a hassle-free approach to dine on-demand. This exactly reflects their taste for time-saving remedies.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2. Nostalgia Factor</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drive-thru brings back memories of family vacations, late-night food runs, and road trips throughout youth. For Millennial, they are a cultural reference point linking them to simpler times rather than only a service.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. Tech-Driven Convenience</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Early digital adopters, millennial have driven-thru changed to fit their needs. For this tech-savvy generation, mobile ordering, app-based promotions, and contactless payments have made drive-through even more enticing.</span></p>\r\n
    <h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Gen Z: The Parking and Walking Generation</span></h2>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Born anywhere between 1997 and 2012, Gen Z approaches convenience differently. Often leading them to park their cars at </span><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="/"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #0563c1; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">East Midlands Airport parking</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> and walk instead of the drive-through, this generation emphasizes experiences, sustainability, and health-conscious choices.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1. Health and Wellness Trends</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">More health-conscious than other generations is Gen Z. Walking to a café or restaurant fits their emphasis on mindful living and physical exercise. They also more likely choose better meal options, which drive-thru sometimes lack.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2. Environmental Awareness</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">A basic value for Generation Z is sustainability. Idling in a drive-thru line adds to carbon emissions; parking and walking lessens their environmental impact. For the betterment of the planet, this generation is ready to give a little convenience sacrifice.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. Experience Over Convenience</span></h3>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Gen Z places experiences above simple convenience. Entering a restaurant lets them mingle with the surroundings, meet employees, and take advantage of the social scene of eating out. To them, the trip is just as vital as the end point.</span></p>\r\n
    <h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">How East Midlands Airport Parking Bridges the Gap</span></h2>\r\n
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">East Midlands Airport Parking has something for everyone, regardless of your generation—Millennial who enjoys drive-through ease or Gen Z-er who prefers parking and strolling.     <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1. </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">East Midlands Airport Parking: Convenience Meets Flexibility</span></h3>\r\n

There is a parking solution for you whether your generation is Gen Z-er who doesn't mind walking a little to save money or Millennial seeking a quick drop-off.</span></p>\r\n
    <h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #404040; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">East Midlands Airport Meet and Greet Parking: Luxury and Ease</span></h3>\r\n
